1419
01:46:57,703 --> 01:46:59,205
I'll be waiting.

1420
01:47:25,105 --> 01:47:26,698
Whiskey on the rocks, huh!

1421
01:47:30,486 --> 01:47:32,284
Greetings, Hamid Gul.

1422
01:47:37,451 --> 01:47:39,124
