is sealed in this transmitter.

1474
01:51:35,230 --> 01:51:37,358
'You're an international
criminal now.'

1475
01:51:39,818 --> 01:51:41,035
'I trust you.'

1476
01:51:43,780 --> 01:51:46,533
'What else did he tell you,
